level.text: The service charge fee for processing an application which has been denied or withdrawn shall be one hundred fifty dollars ($150) for a proprietorship, two hundred fifty dollars ($250) for a partnership, and three hundred fifty dollars ($350) for a corporation or an unincorporated entity.

level.heading: SOURCE
level.text: Final Rulemaking published at 51 DCR 4309 (April 30, 2004); as amended by Final Rulemaking published at 55 DCR 12991 (December 26, 2008).
